inoremap <silent> <C-s> <Esc>:wa<CR>
nnoremap <Leader>q :qa<CR>
inoremap <silent> <C-q> <Esc>:qa<CR>

" Remove white spaces on write
augroup AutoRemoveWhitespace
  autocmd!
  autocmd BufWritePre * :call <SID>RemoveWhitespaces()
augroup END

